-- MOVES-Nicola Foley joins Stonehaven as senior financial controller
-- 
-- Thu Dec 04, 2014 09:09AM EST
-- None



Dec 4 (Reuters) - Stonehaven, a lifetime mortgage provider, appointment chartered accountant Nicola Foley as senior financial controller and company secretary.

Foley will oversee the product suite and develop new products. She will also work closely with the board and assist with the general management of the business.